research_municipality_step.notes: Mansfield, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The Mayor and Council Members are elected at large, and there are no specific council districts. Michael Evans was re-elected Mayor in May 2025, and his term expires in May 2028. Tamera Bounds was re-elected in May 2025, and Todd Simmons was elected in June 2025.
